\newlabel{fig:audit-atlas-summary}{{5}{10}{\textbf {Audit atlas coverage and outcomes.} Each bar summarizes one prediction set in the current atlas. Segments show retained or partial residual signal, background-sensitive rows, sparse or non-interpretable rows and other interpretable outcomes.\relax }{figure.caption.19}{}}
